data.description: Welcome To 2 Tall Pines Ct. In West Nyack, Rockland County. This Beautiful Home Located In Award Winning Clarkstown School District Is The Home You've Been Waiting For. Thoughtfully Designed Cape Cod Boasting Close To 6000 SQ FT Mini-Estate On Builder's Acre Is Perfect For Entertaining and Resort-Style Living. Featuring 6/7 Spacious Bedrooms, 4 1/2 Bathrooms, Recently Installed Heated Floors In Family Room and Bedrooms, Beautiful Gourmet Chef's Kitchen With Large Island, Top Of The Line Appliances, Bright and Spacious Family Room With Skylights And Vaulted Ceilings, Solar Panels, Whole House Generator, Two-Car Garage, Two Driveways, Private Entrance To Legal Accessory Apartment And The Loft Add Convenience For Guests/ Extended Family. Professionally Landscaped & Fully Fenced In Yard With Heated In-Ground Pool Is Exceptional For Large Gatherings And Staycations. Possibliites Are Endless. Must See To Appreciate All The Special Features And Comfort Of This Home Has To Offer!
